            <li>
                <p>
                The population of a city changes over time.
                    <ol>
                        <li>
                            <p>
                            Independent: <response />
                            </p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <p>
                            Dependent: <response />
                            </p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <p>
                            Rate of change: <response />
                            </p>
                        </li>
                    </ol>
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                As a weather balloon rises, the temperature of the air inside (and outside) the balloon decreases.
                    <ol>
                        <li>
                            <p>
                            Independent: <response />
